{"tid":2342281,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗狗可以幾時出街","createTime":"2020-12-27T04:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T04:58:01.000Z","uid":68213,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7c64159d2c0b0817de82eff2a4f1dffc1274eda0","tid":2342281,"uid":68213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T04:23:03.000Z","msg":"聽日打第三針<br />\n而家三個半月大<br />\n使唔使等埋瘋狗症針先帶得佢出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b7dafddad1b20732e76e5f0479e8cf17ffe669","tid":2342281,"uid":294587,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T04:29:01.000Z","msg":"打齊針 最好半歲等佢抵抗力強啲先啦 同周街肺炎出咩街呀"},{"pid":"432eca19175cfd7e944408513f84d5dda4bc10b1","tid":2342281,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:04:11.000Z","msg":"你隨時都出得啦"},{"pid":"7d5556256dea8ad99fb6b125e4eb264f10c85d2f","tid":2342281,"uid":72452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c64159d2c0b0817de82eff2a4f1dffc1274eda0","tid":2342281,"uid":68213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T04:23:03.000Z","msg":"聽日打第三針<br />\n而家三個半月大<br />\n使唔使等埋瘋狗症針先帶得佢出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:13:58.000Z","msg":"正路就要，因為如果發生狗咬狗嘅事有人報狗就會要查狗牌。<br />\n但細狗抵抗力真係好差，加上你聽日先打針，打完最好預多個幾月先好出街啦"},{"pid":"9905c8acbc84c062a40fda0780fa32eba892cf1e","tid":2342281,"uid":68213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12b7dafddad1b20732e76e5f0479e8cf17ffe669","tid":2342281,"uid":294587,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T04:29:01.000Z","msg":"打齊針 最好半歲等佢抵抗力強啲先啦 同周街肺炎出咩街呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:31:10.000Z","msg":"打齊係3針定連埋瘋狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6482597779fadaf497004892d25cffdd167869b1","tid":2342281,"uid":146119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T04:40:35.000Z","msg":"打完3針 瘋狗症針 之後仲有冇針打"},{"pid":"b1504c6e5a73e776e1d1e1c813bb6b13a5379742","tid":2342281,"uid":248699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T04:42:44.000Z","msg":"打齊針 最好差不多一歲先落街散步 平時就喺屋企玩跑下"},{"pid":"5381797a0d46e2fd9363bb17edb0597bddb4669b","tid":2342281,"uid":104424,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T04:58:01.000Z","msg":"狗狗5-6月大係黃金期，要教好社會化就要趁呢個時期，我覺得唔好好似上面講成一歲先出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過安全啲就打埋瘋狗症針先落地行，打完3針可以抱住狗狗出去，帶佢見識同接觸一下出面啲事物，等佢真係正式落地行嘅時侯都冇咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果話驚肺炎的話，每次返嚟用乾洗泡泡抹身同腳就OK"}]}